[The BBC article includes a map.

Results of the epidemiological investigations into the source of
infection are anticipated. At present, 2 scenarios seem to be
considered: introduction by means of imported materials/animals (see
2nd newswire above), or contact of the free-range domestic birds
(turkeys/geese/ducks) with infected wild birds, most likely migratory
water birds. - Mod.AS]
